Authors of ChiiEdit

ChiiEdit was created by Tom Ice <contact@thomasice.com>

A big THANK YOU goes to:
    Salvatore Sanfilippo <antires@gmail.com>
    * Original creator of the 1000 LoC text editor written in C

    Jeremy Ruten <jeremy.ruten@gmail.com>
    * Creator of the step-by-step guide to building your own text editor
      which can be found at https://viewsourcecode.org/snaptoken/kilo/

    Glen Cornell <glen.m.cornell@gmail.com>
    * Creator of original implementation of how cmdline args, version numbers,
      and embedded info are processed in this application, as well as my
      overall embedded development and board support mentor

